    "en": {
      "title": "Clues about a petrol ship from the minister",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Mr. Kanchana Wijesekera, Minister of Electricity and Energy, has stated at the cabinet meeting held last night (04) that a petrol ship will be received in Sri Lanka by the 13th.",
        "The Minister has mentioned that the necessary money has been paid for that.",
        "Meanwhile, Minister Wijesekera has informed the Cabinet that he will make a statement today (05) in the Parliament regarding the upcoming program regarding fuel importation."
      ],
